These virtual labs originated from the teaching experiences when I was the lab instructor of GEOG526 in the Department of Geography and Atmosphere Science, University of Kansas.
Lab 1  talks about entry operations of ERDAS. 
Lab 2  talks about analysis of two Landsat images
Lab 3 talks about viewing digital imagery and understanding digital numbers. 
Lab 4 is about multispectral analysis of images. 
Lab 5 is about supervised and unsupervised classification. 
Lab 6 talks about MODIS Time series. 
